The bad boys of RnB: Jodeci

Jodeci was a very successful band in the 90ies, they were one of the first groups to bring Hip-Hop to RnB. New Jack Swing was born, a highly influencial musical style for todays Black Music. Artists like Missy Elliott (listen to her freestyling on these albums), Timbaland, Ginuwine made their first step into the public eye on Jodeci's albums. Puffy's first very successful steps were with Uptown-records, Jodeci's label. He produced some of their songs.

